import React from "react";
import {Button,Input,Layout,Col, Row,Form} from "antd";
import {Counter} from "./counter";
import {FormHolder} from "./styled";
export const Counters = () =>{
    const { Header,  Content } = Layout;

    return (
    <Layout>
        <Header>
            <FormHolder>
                <Form > 
                    <Row gutter={32}  >                            
                            <Col span={8}   >
                                <Input type="text" placeholder={'please enter step value'} />

                            </Col>
                            <Col span={2}   >
                                <Button danger type="primary" htmlType={'submit'}  >Add Counter</Button>
                            </Col>                
                    </Row>
                </Form>
            </FormHolder>
        </Header>
        <Content>
            <Row gutter={16}>

                <Col span={8}>  
                    <Counter step={1} />
                </Col>

            </Row>
        </Content>
    </Layout>
    )
}
